3 SECTION 4. NEW LAW A new section of law not to be
4 codified in the Oklahoma Statutes reads as follows:
5 The Oklahoma Water Resources Board may enter into memorandums of
6 understanding with other agencies of the State of Oklahoma for the
7 auditing, documentation, evaluation, implementation, oversight,
